    "attributes": {
        "action": "Pay frontline staff a benefit who had COVID-19 due to their work and recovered",
        "additional_details": "All lives are put at risk working as frontline staff and I think those staff who are positive COVID patients, fought off the virus and have gone back to work in their frontline roles should get a recognised benefit by the government",
        "background": "As the government has passed the following; New guarantee on death in service benefits for frontline health and care staff during pandemic. I think it should consider giving all frontline staff a benefit for contracting the virus due to their work",
